               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Giyorgis “Miracles of George”: three miracles (fols.
                     3ra-6rb)
 II) Lectionary (fols. 7ra-8vb)
 
 The Ms. consists of
                     fragments of three different codices (fols. 1-2 and 9 attached to a wooden
                     board; fols. 3ra-6rb and fols. 7ra-8vb) put together without sewing.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
